merku thodarchi malai is an upcoming indian tamil feature film directed by debutant lenin bharathi .   produced by actor vijay sethupathi , the film features newcomers in the lead and has music by isaignani ilaiyaraaja .   the film has been selected as one among 18 films for 21st international film festival of kerala .   it already selected for the best cinematography award at bioscope global film festival , punjab .   in ifft 2017 ( 12th international film festival of thrissur ) the film has been selected for k w joseph all india debut film competition/merku thodarchi malai has been won the kw joseph award in ifft 2017 for best film in the competition .   the film has been nominated for best screenplay category in 17th new york indian film festival ( nyiff2017 ) .